---

---

<section id="about" class="about">
	<div class="about-inner">
		<div class="about-content">
			<span class="section-tag">About</span>
			<h2>An AI-first product<br />company</h2>
			<p>
				AlgoNest Labs is an early-stage software company building AI-powered
				products and platforms. We operate as an umbrella — shipping our own
				SaaS products and mobile apps while helping other companies build
				theirs through consulting and engineering services.
			</p>
			<p>
				Our stack is cloud-native from day one. We deploy on modern cloud
				infrastructure — containers, serverless functions, edge networks,
				GPU compute, and managed databases — to deliver fast, reliable,
				and scalable products to users worldwide.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="about-values">
			<div class="value">
				<div class="value-number">01</div>
				<div class="value-content">
					<h4>AI at the core</h4>
					<p>Every product we build leverages AI — from LLM inference and ML models to intelligent automation.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="value">
				<div class="value-number">02</div>
				<div class="value-content">
					<h4>Cloud-native by default</h4>
					<p>Scalable infrastructure, edge delivery, and auto-scaling compute for production workloads.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="value">
				<div class="value-number">03</div>
				<div class="value-content">
					<h4>Ship fast, iterate faster</h4>
					<p>We build in public, deploy continuously, and let user feedback drive the product forward.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="value">
				<div class="value-number">04</div>
				<div class="value-content">
					<h4>Build our own products</h4>
					<p>We're not just consultants — we operate our own SaaS and mobile products in production.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.about {
		padding: 6rem 2rem;
	}

	.about-inner {
		max-width: var(--max-width);
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 5rem;
		align-items: start;
	}

	.section-tag {
		display: inline-block;
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--color-accent-light);
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.about-content h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.about-content p {
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.75;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.about-values {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.value {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.25rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: var(--color-bg-card);
		border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
		border-radius: 12px;
		transition: border-color 0.2s;
	}

	.value:hover {
		border-color: var(--color-border-hover);
	}

	.value-number {
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		color: var(--color-text-dim);
		padding-top: 0.15rem;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.value-content h4 {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
	}

	.value-content p {
		font-size: 0.825rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
	}

	@media (max-width: 800px) {
		.about-inner {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 3rem;
		}
	}
</style>
